Package: fasthurdle
Type: Package
Title: Fast Implementation of Hurdle Models
Version: 1.1.1
Date: 2026-03-09
Authors@R: person("Masahiro", "Kanai", email = "mkanai@broadinstitute.org",
    role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides fast hurdle regression models for count data using C++
    implementations via 'Rcpp'. Supports the same functionality as the hurdle
    function in the 'pscl' package, with improved performance for large datasets.
